          { "feature": "progressive_waxing_waning", "weight": 3 }
        ],
        "management": "Topical corticosteroids (mometasone) on face and thin skin. Topical calcineurin inhibitors (tacrolimus) for sensitive areas. NB-UVB phototherapy 2-3x/week. Excimer laser for localized."
